Req. No. 17349 Page 4

1 (4) Tier 4: More than ten (10) acres up to twenty
2 (20) acres, the fee shall be Twenty Thousand
3 Dollars ($20,000.00),
4 (5) Tier 5: More than twenty (20) acres up to thirty
5 (30) acres, the fee shall be Thirty Thousand
6 Dollars ($30,000.00),
7 (6) Tier 6: More than thirty (30) acres up to forty
8 (40) acres, the fee shall be Forty Thousand
